育文化背景能夠使他們利用更多媒介獲取信息，對有關事情有更多瞭解，知識面也就比較廣，也使他們具有較強的判斷能力和主觀見解，對各種事物和現象能做出合理判斷和解釋，處理問題較為理智和恰當，易得到別人信任，因而容易說服別人。<br />\n<br />\n　　2．<strong>交際廣泛，同公眾聯繫密切</strong>，有較高的威望。意見領袖大多數社交能力比較強，交游廣泛，有眾多的社會關係，同時又平易近人，易與人接觸，與公眾聯繫比較密切。因為大多博才多學，見多識廣，能對群體成員提供有益的信息和意見，在群體有較高威信，擁有較大的影響力和號召力。<br />\n<br />\n　　3．<strong>具有較高的社會經濟地位</strong>。意見領袖大多收人水平高，而且穩定，這是他們之所以成為意見領袖的經濟基礎。良好的經濟條件使他們有能力成為新廣告產品的早期採用者，獲取有關產品知識。當然，意見領袖的社會經濟地位不能比追隨者過高，否則，相差懸殊，相互間無法溝通，其影響力也就會喪失。<br />\n<br />\n　　4．<strong>樂於創新</strong>。意見領袖思想活躍，性格外向，勇於創新，敢於接受新生事物。尤其是當整個社會倡導革新開放時，其創新精神更為突出，這也是他們成為新觀念、新產品帶頭者、鼓動者的一個重要內因。<br />\n<br />\n敢問得幾千，幾百個like嘅港女有幾多個符合到上面其中兩點呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n莫講話加多個key字係前面啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbbca43099887b4688898956f0ed31fed05d71ad","tid":339523,"uid":38271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T02:54:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實係點解？真係唔明時下用語</blockquote><br />\n意見領袖(Opinion Leader)的特征:<br />\n　　1．<strong>生活經驗豐富，知識面廣</strong>。意見領袖閱歷廣，生活經驗比較豐富，大多數的教育文化程度比較高。良好的教育文化背景能夠使他們利用更多媒介獲取信息，對有關事情有更多瞭解，知識面也就比較廣，也使他們具有較強的判斷能力和主觀見解，對各種事物和現象能做出合理判斷和解釋，處理問題較為理智和恰當，易得到別人信任，因而容易說服別人。<br />\n<br />\n　　2．<strong>交際廣泛，同公眾聯繫密切</strong>，有較高的威望。意見領袖大多數社交能力比較強，交游廣泛，有眾多的社會關係，同時又平易近人，易與人接觸，與公眾聯繫比較密切。因為大多博才多學，見多識廣，能對群體成員提供有益的信息和意見，在群體有較高威信，擁有較大的影響力和號召力。<br />\n<br />\n　　3．<strong>具有較高的社會經濟地位</strong>。意見領袖大多收人水平高，而且穩定，這是他們之所以成為意見領袖的經濟基礎。良好的經濟條件使他們有能力成為新廣告產品的早期採用者，獲取有關產品知識。當然，意見領袖的社會經濟地位不能比追隨者過高，否則，相差懸殊，相互間無法溝通，其影響力也就會喪失。<br />\n<br />\n　　4．<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">樂於創新</span></strong>。意見領袖思想活躍，性格外向，勇於創新，敢於接受新生事物。尤其是當整個社會倡導革新開放時，其創新精神更為突出，這也是他們成為新觀念、新產品帶頭者、鼓動者的一個重要內因。<br />\n<br />\n敢問得幾千，幾百個like嘅港女有幾多個符合到上面其中兩點呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n莫講話加多個key字係前面啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n淨係第四點，香港有9成自稱KOL可以消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d7433ca644a095a8fad9c96158a52a2dce513fb","tid":339523,"uid":133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T02:54:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/30/105436_c38fc3ba97e79d4dc14133597a0b7033.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F30%2F105436_c38fc3ba97e79d4dc14133597a0b7033.PNG&h=e45818a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d6ceddf4f82c9c5d128ee1298f03b740f0dc9521","tid":339523,"uid":133,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T03:03:31.000Z","msg":"我SEARCH下GOOGLE by time range.KOL 應該係強國用先<br />\n<br />\n6月1號出現係Google Hong Kong <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ptl-group.com/blogs/en/kol-key-opinion-leaders\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptl-group.com%2Fblogs%2Fen%2Fkol-key-opinion-leaders&d=VFChOwYL9hlg7MsFh4RdmKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=6e14fe84\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ptl-group.com/blogs/en/kol-key-opinion-leaders</a><br />\n<br />\n之後毒果係7月10號報完就開始爆升.<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/columnist/6257110/art/20160710/19688397\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Fcolumnist%2F6257110%2Fart%2F20160710%2F19688397&d=VFChOwYL9hlg7MsFh4RdmKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=a8ff0302\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Fcolumnist%2F6257110%2Fart%2F20160710%2F19688397&h=cbb2157b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/columnist/6257110/art/20160710/19688397</a>"},{"pid":"2506e431008e227dd4f0072df8d7f2e178765444","tid":339523,"uid":2500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T03:23:44.000Z","msg":"意思讀書教opinion leader<br />\n無左個key<br />\n有無人可以解釋點解會咁"},{"pid":"989101ff3ec829672a36a3c71e353236b13f97e1","tid":339523,"uid":14201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T03:30:22.000Z","msg":"係TVB係咁用KOL呢個term<br />\n之後先多人用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家youtuber呢D字已經開始少左人用"},{"pid":"3f99e82e035b7754ac8c61d03db686012c4dced9","tid":339523,"uid":1301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T03:32:50.000Z","msg":"我覺得鳩達用 鳩噏撚 黎解釋呢個term 幾好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2be1242ce8377c473674cde4a616c02ca420e85","tid":339523,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T03:35:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>KOL = key opinion leader<br />\n你咁撚柒，我唔會笑你</blockquote><br />\n而定個撚個都叫自己KOL<br />\n有幾key 睇商<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76889d2ead50de44196a63bf91f9dfd67ab1f6a9","tid":339523,"uid":52881,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T03:58:10.000Z","msg":"定義本身係冇問題嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過香港好多有三至四位數follower就自稱自己係就好撚柒囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你話可以一直留喺自己個專業範圍上講野的話，的確可以做到KOL嘅功能<br />\n<br />\n不過多數呢類人慣左一呼百應，一講D自己唔係最擅長嘅議題嗰陣就多數衝出來柒，俾真正專業人士指正完之後一係就del post一係就潛水完全唔理個post,過兩日扮無事講過第二D野，一係就好撚有性格話I don't fucking care你班刁民，唔鍾意可以唔睇etc <br />\n<br />\n呢方面健吾真係表表者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講自己嘅領域真係頭頭是道學到野(日本野)<br />\n講D八婆野就柒到核爆(坤哥，etc)<br />\n<br />\n真係多人follow嘅講野都唔負責任，點可能要求班so called KOL 嘅人一樣可以咁大方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講到底有一班人就係靠呢個角色搵到食R到著數，你叫佢認錯即係斷自己米路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e98186d6982a3252feb772b4dc7cab4aaae1127","tid":339523,"uid":78726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T03:59:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>引用</blockquote>一"},{"pid":"6d5f0a67862de368f0b7d7e08dd68854dfc90f63","tid":339523,"uid":16915,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T04:09:28.000Z","msg":"呢個term不嬲得大陸狗用，唔知做乜鳩而家香港都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 係大陸返過工 啲同事成鳩日講呢個term"},{"pid":"3dc91019b73648f31910d14a39870ec61d043e0d","tid":339523,"uid":38550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T04:23:48.000Z","msg":"香港好多嘢都鍾本末倒置<br />\n<br />\n原本有獨特見解o既人往往可以向其他人提供意見甚至帶領走向<br />\n繼而成為KOL<br />\n<br />\n依家就係無論咩人用任何方法上咗位之後求其做啲嘢就叫KOL<br />\n無論係因為派膠上位賣波罅還是燒錢谷廣告谷宣傳<br />\n有人氣之後痾舊屎都可以叫通便KOL"},{"pid":"616f847779e031cc16e122df4232b87adfdcd101","tid":339523,"uid":19217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T04:38:33.000Z","msg":"KOL = 大台<br />\n點解無人反？"},{"pid":"80f6bcffa36f8ac887c474bdc20877835cb795f2","tid":339523,"uid":21052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T04:43:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又係TVB用到柒晒<br />\n所有野去到TVB度都會玩到冇癮</blockquote><br />\n你又講得岩喎<br />\n咩chok 呀 面都紅晒呀 都係tvb一肆宣傳到柒晒"},{"pid":"eb3bcb61c39273752bd3dc468b6cab74cfc45143","tid":339523,"uid":21052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T04:44:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>又係TVB用到柒晒<br />\n所有野去到TVB度都會玩到冇癮</blockquote><br />\n你又講得岩喎<br />\n咩chok 呀 面都紅晒呀 都係tvb大肆宣傳到柒晒</blockquote>"},{"pid":"08c722227397cba2658afbf75ea7739312012673","tid":339523,"uid":19657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T04:45:59.000Z","msg":"足龍屬（學名：Kol）是獸腳亞目阿瓦拉慈龍科恐龍的一屬，生存於白堊紀晚期的蒙古。模式種是美足龍（K. ghuva），屬名在蒙古語意為「腳」，而種名意為「美麗的」。<br />\n<br />\n以後叫佢地做恐龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b8b8848ec34bc3b59407017512484bed5f3b03a","tid":339523,"uid":20820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T04:47:50.000Z","msg":"我成日以為King of 唔知乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9286b42dd9dfc49408c375d11e39a7e2c51425d","tid":339523,"uid":87254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T04:49:23.000Z","msg":"讀大學marketing course 都會有講KOL