gmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a6fce7fbbaa872134e2f086fd6b6985b3416dbb","tid":339523,"uid":38671,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T04:54:28.000Z","msg":"同「女神」一樣<br />\n阿豬阿狗都係kol都係女神"},{"pid":"9ad809b74ab96b2ba784d5915f69fe82419cc721","tid":339523,"uid":29781,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T05:09:45.000Z","msg":"有讀過marketing應該知咩黎<br />\n呢個字不嬲都有 不過d人亂鳩咁用"},{"pid":"a707f9f65c83076740d26c73c802d2e37460aabe","tid":339523,"uid":42009,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T05:15:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>KOL唔會用黎自詡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俾條百婆容祖兒同tvb用到錯撚晒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n馬天佑個D咪自詡囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，<br />\n仲有好多人根本唔知KOL係乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又話乜唔係Marketing 用語咩？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係乜都衝出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32d1c64326ecdf159a3d08ada0c32160bf1210ee","tid":339523,"uid":68837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T05:39:52.000Z","msg":"啲客鐘意點聽咪點叫囉<br />\n佢哋鐘意叫班撚屌做大碌撚我哋咪叫佢哋做大碌撚囉<br />\n有咩鳩唔鳩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f42e9b162218a617f35fa256c6f86b5e92e3c1cc","tid":339523,"uid":21746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T05:46:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>瓊jer個啲叫KOL 講下花生又加自己意見<br />\n賣廣告既就加幾句垃圾範本句子就話自己係KOL<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲KO去晒邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 莫講係咪L<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢條臭閪一言堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n過街老鼠過檔fb畀人推上神枱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌佢老母喺facebook又搞埋啲心心嬲嬲投票選十大演技差嘅藝人又剩 然後又將啲二手圖p啲字加句caption當自己嘢 偏偏大撚把人鍾意呢味唔洗用腦諗嘅嘢"},{"pid":"f08af2261c5547d6de21a6059a6777179a3be303","tid":339523,"uid":19151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T05:59:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實係點解？真係唔明時下用語</blockquote><br />\n意見領袖(Opinion Leader)的特征:<br />\n　　1．<strong>生活經驗豐富，知識面廣</strong>。意見領袖閱歷廣，生活經驗比較豐富，大多數的教育文化程度比較高。良好的教育文化背景能夠使他們利用更多媒介獲取信息，對有關事情有更多瞭解，知識面也就比較廣，也使他們具有較強的判斷能力和主觀見解，對各種事物和現象能做出合理判斷和解釋，處理問題較為理智和恰當，易得到別人信任，因而容易說服別人。<br />\n<br />\n　　2．<strong>交際廣泛，同公眾聯繫密切</strong>，有較高的威望。意見領袖大多數社交能力比較強，交游廣泛，有眾多的社會關係，同時又平易近人，易與人接觸，與公眾聯繫比較密切。因為大多博才多學，見多識廣，能對群體成員提供有益的信息和意見，在群體有較高威信，擁有較大的影響力和號召力。<br />\n<br />\n　　3．<strong>具有較高的社會經濟地位</strong>。意見領袖大多收人水平高，而且穩定，這是他們之所以成為意見領袖的經濟基礎。良好的經濟條件使他們有能力成為新廣告產品的早期採用者，獲取有關產品知識。當然，意見領袖的社會經濟地位不能比追隨者過高，否則，相差懸殊，相互間無法溝通，其影響力也就會喪失。<br />\n<br />\n　　4．<strong>樂於創新</strong>。意見領袖思想活躍，性格外向，勇於創新，敢於接受新生事物。尤其是當整個社會倡導革新開放時，其創新精神更為突出，這也是他們成為新觀念、新產品帶頭者、鼓動者的一個重要內因。<br />\n<br />\n敢問得幾千，幾百個like嘅港女有幾多個符合到上面其中兩點呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n莫講話加多個key字係前面啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔撚係呀嘩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔講真係唔知，香港真係唔係幾配用呢個用語，莫講話自冠為所謂kol"},{"pid":"7fc6b471f1ab0a8d92ab6c9ee3dcae170a8ba579","tid":339523,"uid":131622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T06:11:48.000Z","msg":"以為KOL解King Of Laugh<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28c394cd24caa68fbc37509d13864b7d3f9a3eeb","tid":339523,"uid":71063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T06:12:24.000Z","msg":"一個marketing 詞語比班mk搞到柒曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cec43b2572691bada3c5b42dc0bfdc5d9ea1e7dc","tid":339523,"uid":121058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T06:16:11.000Z","msg":"淨係見過D外國財經雜誌用呢個字(opinion leader)<br />\n而且係指D好猛料既人 <br />\n香港三唔識七都KOL 見到都好尷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dcee98cb3d307a8ea3276b0f8d30aa18576d01a","tid":339523,"uid":120537,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T06:23:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>淨係見過D外國財經雜誌用呢個字(opinion leader)<br />\n而且係指D好猛料既人 <br />\n香港三唔識七都KOL 見到都好尷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知啲無正職嘅所謂KOL點樣講自己職業：<br />\n<br />\n  你好陳生，請問你做邊行？<br />\n  我係一個KOL <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n剩係諗下都覺得好老尷"},{"pid":"71b806eaed547ae6c56bd8712afc50f5d7439634","tid":339523,"uid":48,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T06:28:43.000Z","msg":"我一開頭以為KOL係泡菜傳過黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ed0b79ff387352b468aca0ade225aa8e38a0d3e","tid":339523,"uid":3742,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T07:15:46.000Z","msg":"用網紅都好聽過kol"},{"pid":"02fe541c314f628b04162e159a64fc2197b7a705","tid":339523,"uid":33448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T07:16:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><bl