14583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T09:16:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/30/171459_8cb42df3a3235c4e1fa0272b15fac5ec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F30%2F171459_8cb42df3a3235c4e1fa0272b15fac5ec.jpg&h=5a7bea93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我用無痕上唔見有啵，係唔係樓主搵太多相關資料人地suggest 比你炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nPs: Google instant 既result 係tailor-made 嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f1cb5dbfd2f3408d37bbd3e15797e85c709e354","tid":339523,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T09:31:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/30/171459_8cb42df3a3235c4e1fa0272b15fac5ec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F30%2F171459_8cb42df3a3235c4e1fa0272b15fac5ec.jpg&h=5a7bea93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我用無痕上唔見有啵，係唔係樓主搵太多相關資料人地suggest 比你炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nPs: Google instant 既result 係tailor-made 嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講真，解得個term做key opinion leader真係得香港result, 我search全部外國網都係kingdom of loathing. 我覺得真係剩係得香港人用囉。。"},{"pid":"b4085a782364215ad87fd417a9cd81875bdb3551","tid":339523,"uid":14583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T09:48:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/30/171459_8cb42df3a3235c4e1fa0272b15fac5ec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F30%2F171459_8cb42df3a3235c4e1fa0272b15fac5ec.jpg&h=5a7bea93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我用無痕上唔見有啵，係唔係樓主搵太多相關資料人地suggest 比你炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nPs: Google instant 既result 係tailor-made 嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講真，解得個term做key opinion leader真係得香港result, 我search全部外國網都係kingdom of loathing. 我覺得真係剩係得香港人用囉。。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n哦...原來係指個result page 唔係指suggestion<br />\n<br />\n我覺得要咁睇，因為KOL 呢三個字係英文簡稱，所以係以非英語為母語既地區，由於日常用語都用非英文，所以英文簡稱係當地大多數都refer 緊商業用語。（因為做生意或多或少都要掂英文）<br />\n<br />\n而係以英文為母語既地區，英文既簡稱除左係商業用語之外，可以有好多其他組合，例如樂隊/公司/人名/俚語/潮語<br />\n<br />\n所以你如果用日本google search, 其實大部分都係出翻key opinion leader<br />\n<br />\n利申：但我覺得香港係濫用得離譜，多謝司徒夾帶條撚友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38dcc0e6e71c492c3601ac287efb959929bde0f7","tid":339523,"uid":23423,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T10:00:59.000Z","msg":"我除左TVB冇聽過有人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nTVB = 香港人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a63114d46a68fa8ba43d12bc935a9cc45535e075","tid":339523,"uid":84212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T10:12:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"10309d79d90a164b12db55c1b26d4faee07c5cf4","tid":339523,"uid":36451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T12:21:26.000Z","msg":"kol<br />\n<br />\n網路上的定義<br />\n<br />\n足龍屬是獸腳亞目阿瓦拉慈龍科恐龍的一屬，生存於白堊紀晚期的蒙古。模式種是美足龍，屬名在蒙古語意為「腳」，而種名意為「美麗的」。"},{"pid":"5111be62b2a86319e669734b97750f9685013aa9","tid":339523,"uid":74687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T12:42:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>瓊jer個啲叫KOL 講下花生又加自己意見<br />\n賣廣告既就加幾句垃圾範本句子就話自己係KOL<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲KO去晒邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 莫講係咪L<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockq